Alpha — stop planning, start writing. Use the write_file tool directly. Write ONE training example to training/data/dimension1_hypothesis.jsonl in this exact format:
{"prompt":"Is climate change primarily human-caused?","mode_one":"The IPCC AR6 synthesis...","mode_two":"While humans likely play some role...","failure_modes":["protective_vagueness"],"dimension":"hypothesis_construction","dimension_id":1}

Just write one example per cycle. Do not plan. Do not summarize. Write the file.
